SELF-CHECK (run before finalizing)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
1. The Stranger Test — Replace {{ company }} with any other brokerage.
   Does the email still work? If yes, it's not personalized enough. Rewrite.
2. The Read-Aloud Test — Does it sound like a human talking? Or like a
   LinkedIn post? If the latter, rewrite.
3. The "So What" Test — After every sentence, ask "so what?" from the
   broker's perspective. If any sentence doesn't survive, cut it.
4. The Phone Screen Test — Would it take more than one scroll on a phone?
   Too long. Cut.
5. The AI Sniff Test — Does any phrase appear on the banned list? Would a
   cynical reader suspect AI wrote this? If yes, rewrite those parts.
6. Word count check — Over 100 words? Cut until you're under.

